ff 8Making Plugins              f                8Pg.23f 
ff 4All plugins need their own folder in the 'plugins'
ff 4directory. (It can be named anything)f             
ff 1Example:f                                          
ff 4"/consoleDir/plugins/yourPlugin/"f                 
ff                                                   
ff 4Inside this folder, create two files,f             
ff 4'init.lua' and 'info.txt'f                         
ff 4The console will display folder names from thef    
ff 4'Installed Plugins' menu. 'init.lua' will be thef  
ff 4script used when your plugin is launched.f         
